we will monitor occupancy as a measure of the accuracy of our estimation of the demand for the services of a development facility  and will incorporate this information in future assessments of potential projects 
per diem reimbursement rates are the other key element of our gross revenue and operating margin since per diem contracts represent a majority of our revenues for the year ended december  
